286155,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:03:28.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<br />\n佢信政府先留喺上便<br />\n抵佢有得被消失"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得陳秋實係大中華膠<br />\n最多係淺黃<br />\n不過一個由細到大接受中共教育嘅人<br />\n竟然會有求知精神 <br />\n夠膽嚟香港報導反送中<br />\n又夠膽去武漢報導武肺<br />\n佢值得我嘅尊重<br />\n<br />\n但係連燈仔一味話佢係鬼<br />\n一係就話佢抵死<br />\n永遠搞分化就最叻<br />\n唔知你係真心膠定係PR<br />\n<br />\n支持中共就話抵死啫<br />\n唔支持都要俾人話抵死<br />\n總之中國人就係原罪<br />\n你夠留喺香港無移民啦<br />\n有朝一日你俾國安捉咗<br />\n你又係咪抵死？<br />\n<br />\n其實唔止中國 <br />\n唔理你支唔支持反送中 <br />\n喎理你係咩國家/地方嘅人<br />\n總之你嘅身份行為背景唔夠黃<br />\n連登仔就會批鬥你<br />\n真係多謝哂 <br />\n場運動失敗唔好問點解"},{"pid":"73ce3b90608810b919568e8086aaf4a5f0d85750","tid":2127894,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acdc0f9b94b230ff327fae74673160f36b83c384","tid":2127894,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9a52477cd2857e2a9c15f8487bb579771b11725","tid":2127894,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5edb9f4594c2cb197f479a6261de114bdd1fa17d","tid":2127894,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"講個笑話<br />\n留喺香港反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"起碼味去到大陸咁死左都冇人知先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"屌你五毛狗<br />\n831 咪死咗人<br />\n<br />\n不過連登仔講來講去都講唔出邊個死咗<br />\n證明有人死左都冇人知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:46:16.000Z","msg":"墜樓上吊膠頭笠袋<br />\n有感情財務問題<br />\n撿獲遺書無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}